{"tid":706690,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"今個月辭左職 想問下大假點樣計","createTime":"2018-06-18T05:55:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-18T08:48:57.000Z","uid":44828,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d98d9eb403271c69d595e3e131e28167e3496d4d","tid":706690,"uid":44828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T05:55:20.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我係間公司做左6年 月頭辭左工<br />\n垃圾公司3年先加1日假 <br />\n第6年先有12日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我之前已經請左4日大假，咁我問佢剩抵既大假點處理，佢話我今年未做夠一年當無左。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我上網睇過勞記個網 應該可以計返比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想了解大假係到底係點計  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲埋有無類似個案發生過"},{"pid":"2920d136c8cb230e2ca1907d9455b46425f7d287","tid":706690,"uid":53238,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T05:59:45.000Z","msg":"問 hr 好過啦"},{"pid":"4a3cd48478c34244ee74dac9510ae1899923e835","tid":706690,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T06:02:55.000Z","msg":"六年先加到12日咁西<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d714a74194bf5e52f7a0402aa35b7ad2477ec07","tid":706690,"uid":61795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T06:03:23.000Z","msg":"打去勞工處問"},{"pid":"3c2997dc3a51caa128a03bda62cc727e1748f4ef","tid":706690,"uid":114994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T06:10:45.000Z","msg":"做過6月16咪12日/2囉 ，少過咪少1日<br />\nAnnual leave 由你過probation 果刻就係權利"},{"pid":"66668687005ac33ace12f40e4e2f3f27ea089a33","tid":706690,"uid":44828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T06:15:32.000Z","msg":"我做到7月4號先走<br />\n我話諗住提早兩日走 佢話未夠一年無大假<br />\n我打緊去勞工處，如果真係有 我就交比勞工處處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb4f7a2c3fbc1c36c46a1abc08d789ea732e3fcc","tid":706690,"uid":23303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66668687005ac33ace12f40e4e2f3f27ea089a33","tid":706690,"uid":44828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T06:15:32.000Z","msg":"我做到7月4號先走<br />\n我話諗住提早兩日走 佢話未夠一年無大假<br />\n我打緊去勞工處，如果真係有 我就交比勞工處處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T07:35:48.000Z","msg":"咁你依家即刻請晒佢咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3462dabc5648e6307ef04d5797100bb3eed943a0","tid":706690,"uid":89801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T07:43:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/18/154115_0e59a3812cf8fb93aa207dec2e9921f9.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F18%2F154115_0e59a3812cf8fb93aa207dec2e9921f9.PNG&h=aee9d1de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你6年前入職 你今年做得夠唔夠3個月? 如果今年唔夠3個月就今年可以唔比你<br />\n另外公司有冇用共同假期年? 如果有 係幾月幾日? 如果無 你幾年幾月幾日入職?"},{"pid":"f5d437b2455ab0e7c32cfca3b4c19d374a2dcfec","tid":706690,"uid":171594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T07:54:18.000Z","msg":"公司唔太西正常都肯俾你早幾日走<br />\n橫掂你都辭咗職，個心都唔係份工到<br />\n不過佢唔俾你早走就應該補足錢俾你"},{"pid":"fc4965563b46efaa6b66b78c4353ccb0ec0ca543","tid":706690,"uid":112747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T08:20:43.000Z","msg":"12日,1個月1日,返到6月尾即係6日<br />\n請咗4日剩2日,你同hr夾睇吓早2日走定係計多2日al糧俾你"},{"pid":"9bbbbc5e65b7994a66d84a04ffd8ef7bd6ba322d","tid":706690,"uid":44828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T08:48:57.000Z","msg":"唔講晒巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為細公司 直接同個經理講 比埋張圖佢睇<br />\n佢話去問清楚勞工處先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔小心講左句 咁你問清楚小小<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}